      "span_text": "In addition, to examine whether the automobile industry might have specific agglomeration economies affecting the pattern of manufacturing new plant location, we use state employment in automobile assembly (AUTOEMP). found that auto assembly plants attract supplier plants; however, it is unclear whether this specific effect will show up at the level of aggregation in our research."
